WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.451
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.451 --> 00:00:02.984
How have you all been doing?

00:00:02.984 --> 00:00:05.276
One night I was praying.

00:00:06.104 --> 00:00:11.679
I've told you all that I have puppies sometimes.

00:00:13.235 --> 00:00:23.712
One of my mama dogs was in labor and the puppy was stuck inside of her, and she was not able to get it out.

00:00:23.712 --> 00:00:25.635
It was sideways or something.

00:00:25.950 --> 00:00:32.311
So, I tried to reach up and grab it to get a hold of it to turn it around, but I couldn't turn the dog.

00:00:32.586 --> 00:00:42.160
She was pushing as hard as she could, and I thought she was going to break this puppy in half and kill it because she was pushing so hard.

00:00:42.160 --> 00:00:43.166
Well, there was green.

00:00:43.166 --> 00:00:46.910
You know, if you've ever seen animals born, green is distress.

00:00:47.160 --> 00:00:56.180
It had been going on for hours and it was in the middle of the night during the Christmas holiday, and the vet was gone.

00:00:56.440 --> 00:01:07.660
I couldn't call him to have an emergency C-section to get the puppy out because he was on vacation seeing his kids.

00:01:08.215 --> 00:01:13.679
So, I thought, 'Well, I don't know what to do because we live in a small little town.

00:01:13.679 --> 00:01:17.342
' I didn't know what to do right now other than just pray.

00:01:18.070 --> 00:01:26.205
I was all caught up with fear, thinking, 'Oh no, I'm going to lose the litter.

00:01:26.205 --> 00:01:27.733
I'm going to lose my dog.

00:01:27.733 --> 00:01:32.071
' The devil tried to come and whisper in my ear, 'What are you going to do?

00:01:32.071 --> 00:01:33.316
What are you going to do?

00:01:33.316 --> 00:01:40.027
' You have all these thoughts running through your head at 90 miles an hour about how I could maybe help her.

00:01:43.703 --> 00:01:51.670
You're just stressing out because you see and hear her yelping because she's in so much pain going through labor.

00:01:52.410 --> 00:01:53.520
It was awful.

00:01:53.520 --> 00:01:57.410
So, I just sat in my prayer chair.

00:01:57.680 --> 00:02:08.880
I just bowed my head and said, 'I trust in the Lord with all my heart, and I lean not unto my own understanding, but in all thy ways acknowledge You, and You direct my path.

00:02:08.880 --> 00:02:11.244
You show me what to do, Lord.

00:02:11.244 --> 00:02:13.867
' I just kept saying that over and over.

00:02:13.867 --> 00:02:24.622
'I trust in the Lord with all my heart, and I lean not unto my own understanding, but in all thy ways I acknowledge You, and You said You direct my path.

00:02:24.622 --> 00:02:28.396
' I take the care out of my prayer.

00:02:28.738 --> 00:02:41.546
I know a lot of times when you're going through something hard and you're feeling the pressure of life, everything is going on around you and the circumstances look worse than ever.

00:02:43.093 --> 00:02:47.943
That's why I said, 'God, I take my prayer, and You said be careful for nothing.

00:02:47.943 --> 00:02:55.269
' I kept saying, 'Be careful for nothing, but in everything make your request known unto the Lord.

00:02:55.269 --> 00:02:58.000
' I believe I just butchered that scripture, but that's it.

00:02:59.775 --> 00:03:02.640
I need my Bible; my son has my phone.

00:03:03.947 --> 00:03:16.267
But I kept quoting these scriptures, and with no exaggeration, I probably quoted them several hundred times because it went on for hours into the middle of the night—3:00 in the morning or whenever.

00:03:16.267 --> 00:03:19.742
It was late.

00:03:21.420 --> 00:03:28.239
I just kept quoting the scriptures and praying in the spirit, saying, 'Father, I just trust You.

00:03:28.239 --> 00:03:31.546
God, I thank You that You're moving on my behalf.

00:03:31.546 --> 00:03:36.320
' All of a sudden, it became real to me inside of my spirit.

00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:40.340
I felt a Holy Ghost gusher come out of my spirit.

00:03:40.690 --> 00:03:55.439
I started saying out of my mouth, 'I trust in the Lord with all my heart, and I lean not into my own understanding of what's going on, but in all thy ways I acknowledge You, Lord, and You said You direct my path.

00:03:55.733 --> 00:03:58.960
I tell you, Satan, in the name of Jesus, let go of this!

00:03:59.240 --> 00:04:07.873
I thank You, Father, that the puppy turns around and it's going to be okay, saving the rest of the litter.

00:04:07.873 --> 00:04:15.223
' Usually, whenever a puppy is stuck like that for that long, it's dead.

00:04:17.646 --> 00:04:26.895
I didn't expect this to happen—I'm just telling you—I was just praying for the dog to be okay and not die.

00:04:26.895 --> 00:04:31.736
An angel of the Lord walks through my front door.

00:04:31.736 --> 00:04:35.257
I'm sitting right here; my front door is over there.

00:04:35.257 --> 00:04:41.440
An angel walks through my front door, and she looked female to me.

00:04:41.646 --> 00:04:43.140
It looked like a little girl.

00:04:52.110 --> 00:04:52.580
The angel was about four or five feet tall.

00:05:03.280 --> 00:05:14.365
She walks in wearing a lattice-looking, berry-looking crown-like thing on her head, like a halo.

00:05:15.869 --> 00:05:20.120
Her hair was beautiful blonde.

00:05:21.587 --> 00:05:28.360
She has a little gown on and smiles at me with the greatest grin.

00:05:30.190 --> 00:05:35.840
She was light all over; the glory of the Lord was all over her.

00:05:39.199 --> 00:05:39.812
I was seeing in the spirit, not in the natural.

00:05:44.189 --> 00:05:49.200
I didn't see physical flesh; I'm looking into the spirit and I see this angel go through my door.

00:05:49.600 --> 00:05:54.346
I just grinned back at her because the peace that passes all understanding flooded my home.

00:05:54.772 --> 00:06:01.036
I could feel the presence of the Lord so strong all over me.

00:06:02.015 --> 00:06:18.120
I feel it now when I talk about it manifesting again in my home.

00:06:18.425 --> 00:06:31.690
I got lost in the moment and she just walks right in, kneels down before my little Alice, and she puts her hand on that little dog.

00:06:40.680 --> 00:06:52.770
I saw her bend down on her knees and touch that little dog with her hands, and I kid you not, I heard the loudest pop!

00:06:52.770 --> 00:06:55.376
It sounded like a cork.

00:07:01.982 --> 00:07:02.587
All six puppies came out at once, like a train.

00:07:03.796 --> 00:07:06.587
All of them were alive.

00:07:19.537 --> 00:07:23.044
Not one was dead.

00:07:23.044 --> 00:07:29.328
I helped the mama clean up the dogs and got the sacks off.

00:07:29.680 --> 00:07:34.979
I was just so taken aback at the moment and I just was rejoicing.

00:07:41.467 --> 00:07:41.653
My son was up with me praying over that dog, and he witnessed everything I'm talking about.

00:07:41.653 --> 00:07:44.274
Braden, my son, he witnesses a lot of it.

00:07:44.274 --> 00:07:49.751
All of them came out alive, every single one of them, like a train.

00:07:49.751 --> 00:07:56.735
We got them all cleaned up, and it was a big blessing to this family.

00:08:02.896 --> 00:08:04.000
So, I just wanted to tell you all about that miracle and the angelic encounter I had.

00:08:04.000 --> 00:08:12.916
The Lord brought it up to me again and said, 'I want you to tell my people: use scripture when you pray.

00:08:12.916 --> 00:08:21.405
Find what you're believing for in the Bible, like if it's healing, finances, or a wayward child.

00:08:21.405 --> 00:08:33.519
' I found an amazing scripture where it talks about how the devil blinds the unbelievers' eyes, and we're to pray that the Lord remove the blinders.

00:08:35.075 --> 00:08:35.990
I believe it's in Corinthians.

00:08:35.990 --> 00:08:51.166
Finding scripture to stand on concerning what you're believing for—I just found whatever I could find at that moment.

00:09:03.119 --> 00:09:03.440
It just felt right: 'Trust in the Lord with all your heart.

00:09:03.440 --> 00:09:06.020
' Lean not unto your own understanding.

00:09:06.020 --> 00:09:20.098
Because I was freaking out, I was trying to lean onto my own understanding that all my dogs were going to die and all this was going to happen.

00:09:20.098 --> 00:09:21.769
This was terrible.

00:09:33.749 --> 00:09:34.171
For the mother dog and for everything, it was awful.

00:09:34.171 --> 00:09:47.279
But trying to find a scripture at that moment, that's the only one that came up in my spirit, and it didn't really have anything to do with speaking to the circumstances; it just rolled out of me.

00:09:47.279 --> 00:09:48.559
Just pray that.

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:57.345
But I'm just saying, find a scripture for your situation and pray the word.

00:10:10.390 --> 00:10:10.660
Pray the word concerning what you need.

00:10:22.034 --> 00:10:23.730
Stand on that word.

00:10:23.730 --> 00:10:28.347
Believe it with all your heart and don't let it go.

00:10:28.347 --> 00:10:36.000
Let it become so real to you that it is more real to you; it is Rhema.

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:43.040
It becomes something so alive inside of your spirit because we're not dealing with a fleshly God; we're dealing with a spirit God.

00:10:43.040 --> 00:10:44.400
He is spirit.

00:10:44.400 --> 00:10:52.380
And so we have to operate in the spirit to get what we need in the natural, in the flesh.

00:10:53.080 --> 00:10:57.760
It happens in the spirit before it happens in the natural.

00:10:57.760 --> 00:11:04.320
So what you're looking for in the natural has to be birthed in the spirit first, in prayer.

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:14.709
So when you're praying for something and you're believing for your manifestation, find scripture because the word is what you're going to have to have.

00:11:15.340 --> 00:11:17.680
All this other stuff, the flesh—you get in the flesh.

00:11:17.680 --> 00:11:20.160
God's not moved by our need; He's moved by our faith.

00:11:20.160 --> 00:11:22.994
And I'm going to tell you, if you're begging, you're not believing.

00:11:22.994 --> 00:11:30.229
And you have to get inside the spirit first to get out of the spirit and into the natural.

00:11:30.229 --> 00:11:34.823
I'm going to say that again and again because that's how important it is for you to understand.

00:11:34.823 --> 00:11:39.577
We're not dealing with the natural; we're dealing with the spiritual.

00:11:43.303 --> 00:11:53.154
You have to understand this concerning your unsaved loved ones, concerning your healing, concerning finances, sowing seed.

00:11:58.544 --> 00:11:58.832
It is a lot different with finances.

00:11:59.413 --> 00:12:04.639
I always say I look at it this way: whenever I have a need, I sow a seed.

00:12:04.639 --> 00:12:08.399
When you have a need, you sow a seed.

00:12:09.039 --> 00:12:13.079
I sow and I say, 'Father, I put it into good soil.

00:12:13.079 --> 00:12:17.279
' And I say, 'Father, I thank you, Lord.

00:12:17.279 --> 00:12:19.839
We have a need.

00:12:19.839 --> 00:12:26.800
' Whether it's your electric, water, gas, your car payment, whatever it may be—food for your house, whatever.

00:12:26.800 --> 00:12:29.131
Father, I thank you.

00:12:29.131 --> 00:12:32.476
And it may just be ten cents.

00:12:34.120 --> 00:12:38.044
You go in there and you give that ten cents.

00:12:38.044 --> 00:12:46.343
If the widow's mite moved Jesus more than the rich man giving all that he had, how much more would He be moved for you?

00:12:46.343 --> 00:12:48.613
He's no respecter of persons.

00:12:48.613 --> 00:12:57.223
So even if you just have a penny to give, give it with faith.

00:12:57.223 --> 00:13:06.709
Give it to the Lord in faith, your church offering or whatever you do, give it by faith.

00:13:06.709 --> 00:13:20.519
Even like I said, even if it's two cents and you believe for your manifestation of some thirty, some sixty, and some hundredfold, that's just what we believe.

00:13:20.519 --> 00:13:23.004
What's a hundredfold of two cents?

00:13:26.686 --> 00:13:27.040
And that's where you've got to grow.

00:13:27.040 --> 00:13:35.257
You'll learn how to believe God for five dollars or ten dollars or a hundred dollars or whatever you need.

00:13:43.759 --> 00:13:43.973
It takes time to develop your faith.

00:13:43.973 --> 00:13:57.472
It's like a muscle: you keep working out at the gym, you keep going to the gym, you run on that spiritual treadmill and you start dropping weight.

00:13:57.472 --> 00:14:01.351
You've got to keep on keeping on.

00:14:01.351 --> 00:14:07.480
Whenever it seems like it's not even working, you've got to keep speaking and finding scripture because that's whenever your mountain needs to hear your voice.

00:14:08.128 --> 00:14:14.820
You have to speak to your mountain and tell it, 'Be thou removed, and be thou cast into the sea.

00:14:14.820 --> 00:14:22.280
' And if you shall not doubt in your heart, you shall have whatsoever things you say.

00:14:24.045 --> 00:14:24.639
That's Mark 11:24, somewhere around there.

00:14:24.639 --> 00:14:26.740
So, you can't doubt.

00:14:26.740 --> 00:14:34.079
That's where I have to get in there, and that's where I'm trying to tell you all a lot of it is about grace.

00:14:34.079 --> 00:15:02.560
Because I'm telling you, when the doubt tries to come in and try to rob you of your faith, and you feel your circumstances aren't changing and you keep on keeping on and it seems like all hell's coming against you and you've got all these trials, I'm telling you, that's whenever I've come to figure out—sometimes I just throw my hands up and say, 'Father, it's by Your grace.

00:15:02.560 --> 00:15:04.590
It's all by Your grace.

00:15:04.590 --> 00:15:12.343
' Even where I'm at right now, whenever you say I am weak, You are strong.

00:15:12.343 --> 00:15:14.320
When I am weak, Lord, You're strong.

00:15:18.230 --> 00:15:18.399
And I lay at Your feet.

00:15:18.399 --> 00:15:25.199
Even with all the scripture I've tried to find, You're the only one that's going to fix this.

00:15:25.199 --> 00:15:28.000
I'm just being real with y'all.

00:15:28.000 --> 00:15:31.880
Bottom line is we're all a work in progress.

00:15:31.880 --> 00:15:35.376
None of us have it all figured out.

00:15:35.376 --> 00:15:40.179
We're all trying to work out our salvation with fear and trembling.

00:15:40.179 --> 00:15:42.640
We're all seeking Him every single day.

00:15:49.050 --> 00:15:49.260
And none of us are going to get everything right all the time.

00:15:49.260 --> 00:15:52.491
I'm going to be flat out with you.

00:15:57.379 --> 00:16:03.949
And I've had some really cool visitations, but it comes down to it: it's the grace of God that gets me through every single day.

00:16:03.949 --> 00:16:18.353
It isn't about how much Brandon prays or how elegant I may pray or how I may think that I have it.

00:16:18.353 --> 00:16:24.329
'Well, I prayed that special prayer so Jesus is going to hear me more.

00:16:24.329 --> 00:16:30.160
' No, it's the prayer of faith that will heal the sick.

00:16:30.160 --> 00:16:45.462
It could be someone just says, 'Jesus, heal him,' being some kind of simple little prayer and having faith behind it and getting the manifestation of it.

00:16:58.822 --> 00:16:59.245
It doesn't have to be some kind of elegant theological worded prayer all the time to be perfect.

00:16:59.245 --> 00:17:00.937
Just find scripture.

00:17:00.937 --> 00:17:06.693
Find scripture that pertains to your situation and say a simple prayer about it.

00:17:11.520 --> 00:17:11.920
You don't have to make it all religious.

00:17:11.920 --> 00:17:14.070
Just be real with Jesus.

00:17:14.070 --> 00:17:19.600
When you get real with God, God will get real with you.

00:17:19.600 --> 00:17:23.760
He sees beyond all that baloney.

00:17:23.760 --> 00:17:25.055
He sees beyond all the fleshy stuff.

00:17:25.055 --> 00:17:27.466
He knows the heart.

00:17:27.466 --> 00:17:39.189
The eyes of the Lord are running to and fro throughout the whole earth looking for a heart that is perfect towards Him.

00:17:51.919 --> 00:17:52.212
He's looking for a heart, somebody who has good motives behind what they're saying and how they're praying.

00:17:52.212 --> 00:17:55.609
He knows the motives of why you're praying what you're praying.

00:17:55.609 --> 00:17:56.933
He knows what you're thinking.

00:17:56.933 --> 00:18:00.720
He knows the deep down secret things that you think you're hiding.

00:18:00.720 --> 00:18:08.799
He's looking all the way down into the depths of all your junk and He's looking and going, 'Whatever.

00:18:10.514 --> 00:18:11.497
It's by grace, Brandon.

00:18:11.497 --> 00:18:19.462
' That's why I say a lot of times I'll be praying and I say, 'Listen, Brandon, chill out.

00:18:19.462 --> 00:18:21.386
' You know, calm down.

00:18:21.386 --> 00:18:22.720
'I see what you're going through.

00:18:26.331 --> 00:18:27.166
I understand why you said what you said.

00:18:31.866 --> 00:18:32.400
I understand why you did what you did.

00:18:33.467 --> 00:18:37.531
And I'm merciful to you.

00:18:37.531 --> 00:18:44.754
' His mercies are new every morning and great is His faithfulness to you.

00:18:44.754 --> 00:18:45.646
He understands.

00:18:45.646 --> 00:18:45.943
He loves you.

00:18:45.943 --> 00:18:48.811
He's a good God.

00:18:48.811 --> 00:18:51.028
He's a faithful God.

00:18:51.028 --> 00:18:54.720
And that's what I'm trying to tell y'all.

00:18:54.720 --> 00:18:56.720
That's what I had for y'all today.

00:18:57.620 --> 00:19:00.251
I don't want to take it too long.

00:19:00.251 --> 00:19:01.760
It's 30 minutes.

00:19:01.760 --> 00:19:11.691
I try to keep these short because people just seem to click out.

00:19:11.691 --> 00:19:18.799
But I just want to make sure that you get what the Lord had for you today.

00:19:18.799 --> 00:19:19.729
It's important.

00:19:19.729 --> 00:19:23.931
And so I hope this blessed y'all.

00:19:23.931 --> 00:19:30.799
Let me pray for you, and I'll agree with you that you have your miracle that you're believing for.

00:19:30.799 --> 00:19:33.770
Just like God came through for me, He'll come through for you.

00:19:33.770 --> 00:19:39.942
Father, I just thank You for every single person that is represented here.

00:19:40.919 --> 00:19:45.679
I call healing and wholeness and wellness over their bodies.

00:19:50.480 --> 00:19:53.580
I thank You, Father, that You said in Your word that no weapon formed against them will prosper.

00:19:55.329 --> 00:20:01.440
And I thank you, Father, that you also said that by your stripes, they are healed.

00:20:09.840 --> 00:20:14.240
And I call healing and wholeness and wellness over them in the name of Jesus.

00:20:14.240 --> 00:20:27.733
From the top of their head to the soles of their feet, I call them healed and whole and well in Jesus' name.

00:20:27.733 --> 00:20:35.200
Father, from all kinds of disorders, from fibromyalgia to PTSD to all things, it does not matter.

00:20:35.200 --> 00:20:45.059
From even a hangnail, Lord, you care about it all and you paid the price for every single one of them to walk in divine health.

00:20:45.059 --> 00:20:51.039
So, Father, I thank you, Lord, for manifestations of the glory on their lives today.

00:20:51.382 --> 00:20:57.787
I thank you, Father, for your provision for every single one of them.

00:21:06.964 --> 00:21:08.537
You said in your word that you would supply all our needs according to your riches and glory by Christ Jesus.

00:21:11.200 --> 00:21:17.880
I thank you, Lord, for supernatural harvest over their finances from every single area of their life from 30, 60, and 100-fold.

00:21:32.620 --> 00:21:32.920
I call forth an abundant harvest over their finances in the name of Jesus.

00:21:42.845 --> 00:21:59.942
And I thank you, Father, that every unsaved loved one, every unsaved person that's represented here, Father, needs salvation in their homes; I call their homes filled with the presence of the Lord.

00:22:03.520 --> 00:22:04.800
And we call those wayward people back in the name of Jesus.

00:22:14.150 --> 00:22:14.381
We say, Satan, you take your blinders off of their eyes.

00:22:17.462 --> 00:22:35.595
And we thank you, Lord, that you're bringing in the light that's flooding their eyes, flooding their hearts, and they would know that Jesus Christ loves them, and that he came and he died for them, and he rose again on the third day, and that they don't have to go to hell, the devil's hell.

00:22:35.595 --> 00:22:41.942
They can go to heaven and live for eternity for you, Lord.

00:22:50.520 --> 00:22:57.080
I thank you, Lord, that every single one of them would know you and know you intimately as their Lord and Savior.

00:23:04.869 --> 00:23:05.280
I thank you, Lord, for marriages to be restored.

00:23:05.280 --> 00:23:15.458
I pray for marriages right now and creative ideas for them to get finances for restoration in their finances and for restoration in their homes.

00:23:15.458 --> 00:23:19.680
Lord, you always show me a lot of people fight over money.

00:23:19.680 --> 00:23:24.080
And so, Father, I thank you, Lord, that you bring financial peace over them.

00:23:24.080 --> 00:23:26.320
There'll be peace, Father, that they'll understand who they are and understand what you paid for.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
And that, Father, they can have peace in their homes and joy in their homes.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
We thank you, Lord, that you're bringing restoration in homes and marriages to be stronger than they ever have before.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.750
Father, I thank you, Lord, for their children, for peace in their children, in their schools, and that there is a covering over their schools.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Father, I thank you, Lord, that they're light in darkness.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
And I thank you, Lord, for just delivering their kids from all kinds of perversion.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
And that, Father, you would bring healing to their homes in the name of Jesus.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Father, I thank you, Lord, for new kidneys for Joyce.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
We always believe for kidneys for Joyce and for new hearts and for new brains and new whatever they need.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Alzheimer's is gone, broken off, strokes are healed and whole and well.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
And we thank you, Lord, that we find the scriptures that we need and we pray those scriptures.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.600
We stand on that word because, Father, that's all that matters is the word of God.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
And we put your word priority in our life.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:09.100
And we give you all the glory, honor, and praise for everything you've done for us and what you continue to do on a daily basis.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
And we give you praise and glory for it.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.050
Amen and amen.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
God bless you all.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Have a blessed day and thank you for supporting me.

